videos.description: Gardner-Webb guard Nate Johnson knocks down a corner 3-pointer to increase the Bulldogs' lead to 4.
videos.headline: Johnson hits corner three to increase lead

videos.description: Gardner-Webb's DJ Laster gets out on the break before flying in for the slam dunk.

videos.headline: Laster rises for thunderous slam over Radford
